readme:
Service Usage

This service will notify GOIS of (summarized) integrity entries for a number of categories such as Visa Cancellations , Protection Visa applications, IRIS Refuge and Humanitarian Visa applications

Service Behaviour

CANX sends SV449 and is transformed into SV609 and forwarded to GOIS
ICSE sends SV448 amd is transformed into SV609 and forwarded to GOIS
TRIPS sends 454 and is transformed into SV609 and forwarded to GOIS

The service consolidates and sends a single integrity indcident to GOIS after applying filters and passing summarised information for recording events in GOIS.

This is an asychronis service.

Service Variants

'None'

Service Dependencies

'None'
